summary:
ISSUES
Critical:
- The "How It Works" page failed the web performance test. It is recommended to investigate the cause of this failure and optimize the page's performance to ensure a smooth user experience.
insights: The pricing page and blog page have the fastest load times, indicating effective optimization and efficient page structure.
The time to first byte (ttfb) for all pages is relatively low, suggesting that the server response time is good.
The first contentful paint (fcp) for the homepage is higher than the pricing page and blog page, indicating that the initial rendering of the homepage could be improved.
